content.value: has adopted a privacy policy applicable to personal information collected in connection with the business conducted under that brand. Each privacy policy may be accessed by clicking on the following links:

When you visit our Website, we or one of our third party service providers may place a text file called a cookie in the browser directory of your computers hard drive. A cookie is a small piece of information that a website can store on your web browser and later retrieve information. The cookie cannot be read by any website other than the one that placed the cookie. Some browsers can be set to reject all cookies. If you choose to modify your browser in this manner, some pages of this Website may not function properly.

Upon your activation, these third party service providers may use cookies on our behalf to collect and store Internet log information, such as what time the visits occurred, whether the visitor has been to this site before, and what site referred the visitor to the web page. Geographic data may also determined by the IP Address of the visitors computer. If you activate such function, this information collected by the cookie may be transmitted to our third party service providers and may then be used to evaluate visitors behaviour and to generate statistical reports for the website activity on Sunwing Vacations Groups Website and may be used for marketing purposes.

You can choose to disable cookies in your browser at any time by following the procedure described in the Tools or Preferences menu in your browser. If you choose to modify your browser in this manner, some pages of the Website may not function properly.

, Ottawas premier cover band, dedicated to bringing the iconic sounds of the 80s and 90s back to life. Founded by a group of passionate musicians, our mission is to deliver unforgettable performances that capture the spirit of the music that defined a generation. We play everything from high-energy rock anthems to timeless pop hits, making sure theres something for everyone to sing along to and dance the night away.

Catch us at some of Ottawas most beloved local pubs, where we bring the crowd together for an electric experience filled with energy, nostalgia, and great tunes. Each set is carefully crafted to take you on a journey through the decades, featuring hits from legendary bands and artists that you know and love. With dynamic musicianship and an infectious stage presence, we make sure every performance is one to remember.
Whether youre reliving the soundtrack of your youth or discovering these classics for the first time,
is here to make every night a celebration. Come join the party and lose yourself in the music with us!
